{"sn6.13:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 6.13 ","sn6.13:0.2":"2. Dutiyavagga ","sn6.13:0.3":"Andhakavindasutta ","sn6.13:1.1":"Ekam samayam bhagava magadhesu viharati andhakavinde. ","sn6.13:1.2":"Tena kho pana samayena bhagava rattandhakaratimisayam abbhokase nisinno hoti, devo ca ekamekam phusayati. ","sn6.13:1.3":"Atha kho brahma sahampati abhikkantaya rattiya abhikkantavanno kevalakappam andhakavindam obhasetva yena bhagava tenupasankami; upasankamitva bhagavantam abhivadetva ekamantam atthasi. ","sn6.13:1.4":"Ekamantam thito kho brahma sahampati bhagavato santike ima gathayo abhasi: ","sn6.13:2.1":"“Sevetha pantani senasanani, ","sn6.13:2.2":"Careyya samyojanavippamokkha; ","sn6.13:2.3":"Sace ratim nadhigaccheyya tattha, ","sn6.13:2.4":"Sanghe vase rakkhitatto satima. ","sn6.13:3.1":"Kulakulam pindikaya caranto, ","sn6.13:3.2":"Indriyagutto nipako satima; ","sn6.13:3.3":"Sevetha pantani senasanani, ","sn6.13:3.4":"Bhaya pamutto abhaye vimutto. ","sn6.13:4.1":"Yattha bherava sarisapa, ","sn6.13:4.2":"Vijju sancarati thanayati devo; ","sn6.13:4.3":"Andhakaratimisaya rattiya, ","sn6.13:4.4":"Nisidi tattha bhikkhu vigatalomahamso. ","sn6.13:5.1":"Idanhi jatu me dittham, ","sn6.13:5.2":"nayidam itihitiham; ","sn6.13:5.3":"Ekasmim brahmacariyasmim, ","sn6.13:5.4":"sahassam maccuhayinam. ","sn6.13:6.1":"Bhiyyo pancasata sekkha, ","sn6.13:6.2":"dasa ca dasadha dasa; ","sn6.13:6.3":"Sabbe sotasamapanna, ","sn6.13:6.4":"atiracchanagamino. ","sn6.13:7.1":"Athayam itara paja, ","sn6.13:7.2":"punnabhagati me mano; ","sn6.13:7.3":"Sankhatum nopi sakkomi, ","sn6.13:7.4":"musavadassa ottapan”ti. "}